The '''Travel and Transport Bureau''' was a sub-division of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]]. This committee was responsible for investigating troubles concerning transport ships across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

Delegates from the Travel and Transport Bureau were dispatched to [[Yorn Skot]] to investigate the attempted destruction of the ''[[Aurorient Express]]'', foiled by [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] in [[38 BBY/Legends|38 BBY]].

